Increament & Decreament Operator:->


Expression		initial value of x			value of y			final value of x
y=++x			10							11					11
y=x++			10							10					11
y=--x			10							9					9
y=x--			10							10					9

Loop Hole:->
-> we can apply increament and decreament operators only for variables but not for constant values.
int x = 10;
int y = ++x;
sysout(x);

output:
11

int x = 10;
int y = ++10;
syosut(x);

output:
CE
